headline.print_headline: Briton Wins Stage in Basque Country Race
headline.main: Briton Wins Stage in Basque Country Race

snippet: Stephen Cummings took a tightly bunched leading pack by surprise with a powerful sprint in the last kilometer to win the third stage of the Tour of Basque Country.
lead_paragraph: Stephen Cummings took a tightly bunched leading pack by surprise with a powerful sprint in the last kilometer to win the third stage of the Tour of Basque Country.
